exceptions.tactic: intros X m l H1 H2.
intros X' m l H1 H2.
intros X' m' l H1 H2.
intros X' m' l' H1 H2.

original: intros X m l H1 H2. apply list_has_dup_equiv in H1. apply list_pick in H2. destruct H1 as [x [aa [bb [cc H1]]]]. destruct H2 as [y [l1 [l2 [H2 H3]]]]. exists x, aa, bb, cc. rewrite H1. rewrite H2. auto.
